                   ARP-SH1 GENERAL LIBRARY MANUAL

NAME
    lib/table.moon -- Generate ASCII tables

SYNOPSIS
    Table = use "lib/table.moon"
    Table\addHeader("header")
    Table\addRow({"col"})

DESCRIPTION
    Generate ASCII tables dynamically. The size of the columns are
    determined by the longest string in each column.

    FUNCTIONS

        addHeaders(string)
            Add a header to the table. The only parameter is the
            name of the header to be displayed.
        addRow(table)
            Add a new row to the table. The only parameter is the
            table of strings to display.